---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HeroSection from "../components/Sections/HeroSection.astro";
import EventList from "../components/Sections/EventList.astro";
import SermonList from "../components/Sections/SermonList.astro";
import Button from "../components/UI/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Ariane Mader | Coaching & Counselling"
  seoTitle="ADHD, Procrastination & Stress Coaching | Ariane Mader | Amsterdam, Almere & Online"
  seoDescription="Coaching and counselling for ADHD, neurodivergence, procrastination, overwhelm, stress management, habits, routines, and career clarity. Online coaching and in-person sessions in Amsterdam and Almere, the Netherlands."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.arianemader.com/"
  lang="en"
>
  <HeroSection 
  title="Coaching & Counselling"
  subtitle="For Procrastination, Overwhelm & Building Routines That Stick"
  backgroundImage="/uploads/home-header.png"
/>


<section id="intro-message" class="py-8 bg-white">
  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <h4 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">
          You know what to do — but you just can’t get yourself to do it.
        </h4>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none [&>p]:my-2">
        <p>
          I help you build a way of working that <b>actually fits your brain</b>, so you can follow through without constant stress, guilt, or last-minute panic.
        </p>
        <p>
          I specialize in coaching and counselling for <b>procrastination, overwhelm, stress management, habits, routines, and executive functioning challenges</b>. If traditional productivity advice hasn’t worked for you — or if you’re neurodivergent (e.g. ADHD) — we will figure out what does.
          Whether you want to finally hand in an essay on time, exercise regularly, or stay on top of everyday tasks, we work towards <b>practical, lasting change</b>.</br>
        </p>
        <p>
          Sessions are available online and in person in Amsterdam and Almere.
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="font-medium underline transition-colors text-[#193472] hover:!text-[#30B28E]"
          >Book</a>
          a free intro call.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- General -->
<section id="problem" class="py-8 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="w-full px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
        <div class="max-w-3xl prose prose-lg">
          <p>
            <b>Does this sound familiar?</b>
          </p>

          <ul class="green-bullets space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>You keep putting things off, even when they matter to you</li>
            <li>You start things last minute and end up stressed — again</li>
            <li>You make plans, but somehow don’t follow through</li>
            <li>You feel overwhelmed and don’t know where to start</li>
            <li>You’ve tried to <i>“just be more disciplined”</i>, but it doesn’t stick</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            And underneath it all, there’s this thought: <b>“I know what to do… so why can’t I just do it?”</b><br />
            It can feel like you are wasting your potential and creating unnecessary stress for yourself.
          </p>
        </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          src="/uploads/home-image.jpg"
          alt="Coaching illustration"
          class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-xl"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section id="solution" class="py-8 bg-white">
  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="max-w-none prose prose-lg flex-1">
          <p>
            <b>It does not have to stay this way.</b><br />
            Most advice assumes that the same methods work for everyone. But they don’t.<br />
            Instead, we figure out what works for <i>you</i>. So you can 
            <span class="greenDarkFont">start tasks more easily</span>,
            <span class="greenDarkFont">follow through more consistently</span>,
            <span class="greenDarkFont">build routines that actually stick</span>,
            and
            <span class="greenDarkFont">feel more in control again.</span>
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            <b>We might work on things like:</b>
          </p>
            <ul class="green-bullets my-3 space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>starting and finishing a thesis, portfolio, or work project without getting stuck in avoidance</li>
            <li>building routines for planning, admin, meals, sleep, or exercise that actually fit your life</li>
            <li>managing overwhelm, stress, and resistance before things pile up</li>
            </ul>
          
          <p class="mb-3">
            <b>Through coaching and counselling, we:</b>
          </p>

          <ul class="green-bullets my-3 space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>explore what is getting in your way (including resistance)</li>
            <li>test small, realistic changes</li>
            <li>adjust based on what works and what doesn’t</li>
            <li>build a system that fits your brain, your life, and your goals</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mt-3">
            We will work with a mix of practical tools (habits, structure) and deeper work (patterns, beliefs, values) for
            <span class="greenDarkFont font-semibold">sustainable change</span>.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you recognize yourself in this, we can explore it together.
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="font-medium underline transition-colors text-[#193472] hover:!text-[#30B28E]"
            >Book</a>
            a free intro call to see if we're a good fit.
          </p>
        </div>

                <!-- Image -->
        <div class="hidden md:flex flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src="/uploads/plant2.jpg"
            alt="Coaching atmosphere"
            class="w-56 md:w-64 lg:w-72 h-auto rounded-xl"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Individual Coaching -->
<section id="coaching" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Coaching for Individuals</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      I offer online and in-person coaching in Almere and Amsterdam for personal and professional challenges. Sessions are practical, structured, and tailored to your needs — whether you want short-term clarity, long-term change, or a deep dive into a specific topic.
    </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/coaching" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Workshops -->
<section id="workshops" class="py-12 bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Workshops for Universities & Organisations</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      I also design and deliver tailored workshops for teams, departments, and student groups on a variety of topics. Formats range from short introductions to in-depth interactive sessions.
    </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/workshops" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Me -->
<section id="about" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Why work with me?</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      My style is <b>calm, direct, practical, and empathetic.</b><br>
      I combine an analytical, scientific background with creative thinking and deep interest in how people function. 
      I don’t apply one system to everyone, but help you find what actually works for <i>you</i>.
    </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/about" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
